          • [ - ] StickandMove - member since 02-Oct-15

            For the first team this season Cocu has a fully fit squad. I'm really hoping for Maxime Lestienne- de Jong-Pereiro to play upfront. Cocu will probably hold on to Locadia on the left and he might even prefer Narsingh above Pereiro on the right. Nonetheless, this is a must win game for PSV. They are battling with Ajax for the championship, and their villain face a difficult match on sunday vs AZ. Despite the fact PSV played a intense game earlier this week against Atleti I expect them to win comfortably tonight: 2-0.
